<view class="container" wx:if="{{post}}">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="header">
      <view class="tag tag-{{post.type === '跑腿代办' ? 'runerrand' : post.type === '周边商家' ? 'shop' : post.type === '今日摊位' ? 'stall' : post.type === '二手闲置' ? 'secondhand' : post.type === '拼车拼单' ? 'carpool' : 'other'}}">
        {{post.type}}
      </view>
      <view class="title">{{post.title}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-label">具体内容</view>
      <view class="section-content">{{post.description}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="info-grid">
      <view class="info-item" wx:if="{{post.location}}">
        <view class="info-label">地点</view>
        <view class="info-value">{{post.location}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="info-item" wx:if="{{post.time}}">
        <view class="info-label">时间</view>
        <view class="info-value">{{post.time}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="info-item" wx:if="{{post.price}}">
        <view class="info-label">价格</view>
        <view class="info-value">{{post.price}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section" wx:if="{{post.contact}}">
      <view class="section-label">联系方式</view>
      <view class="section-content" wx:if="{{post.allowPublicContact}}">{{post.contact}}</view>
      <view class="section-content contact-hidden" wx:else>
        该信息未公开联系方式，请通过平台负责人进一步确认
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section" wx:if="{{post.remark}}">
      <view class="section-label">备注</view>
      <view class="section-content">{{post.remark}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="safety-warning">
    <view class="warning-title">安全提示</view>
    <view class="warning-content">
      1. 请仔细核实信息真实性，谨防诈骗
      2. 交易时建议选择校内公共场所
      3. 涉及金钱交易请谨慎，建议当面交易
      4. 如遇可疑信息请及时向平台举报
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
